<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
    <link rel="icon" type="image/png" href="/images/SnugglyBubblyPaws.png">
    <title>Snuggly Bubbly Paws</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.8/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</head>

<body>
    <%- include('partials/header') %>
        <img src="/images/clinic.jpg" alt="Snuggly Bubbly Paws Banner" class="img-fluid mt-3">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="row align-items-center">
                <div class="col-md-8">
                    <h3 class="mt-4">Meet Our Dedicated Team</h3>
                    <h4 class="mt-3">Dr. Jane Smith</h4>
                    <p>
                        Dr. Jane Smith graduated from the National University of Singapore in 2008, she has built her
                        veterinary career through years of experience in small animal practice across Singapore. She has
                        a strong passion for veterinary dentistry and is dedicated to helping pet owners understand the
                        importance of maintaining good oral health for their furry companions.
                        <br><br>
                        She is currently furthering her knowledge through a distance Master of Veterinary Medicine
                        programme with Massey University, with the goal of continuing to develop her expertise and
                        eventually achieving further qualifications in veterinary dentistry. Outside of work, she enjoys
                        aquascaping, keeping ornamental fish, and spending quality time with her cats and parrots.
                    </p>
                </div>

                <div class="col-md-4 text-end">
                    <img src="/images/drjane.jpg" alt="Dr. Jane Smith" class="img-fluid mt-4 float-end"
                        style="width: 300px;">
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="row align-items-center">
                <div class="col-md-4 text-center">
                    <img src="/images/dr-emily-tan.jpg" alt="Dr. Emily Tan" class="img-fluid rounded shadow">
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-8">
                    <!-- Your headings and paragraph here -->
                    <h4 class="mt-3">Dr. Emily Tan</h4>
                    <p>
                        Dr. Emily Tan graduated from the University of Sydney in 2012 and has since gained extensive
                        experience in small animal practice across Singapore. She has a strong passion for veterinary
                        dentistry and is dedicated to
                        helping pet owners understand the importance of maintaining good oral health for their furry
                        companions.
                        <br><br>
                        She is currently furthering her knowledge through a distance Master of Veterinary Medicine
                        programme with Massey University, with the goal of continuing to develop her expertise and
                        eventually achieving further qualifications in veterinary dentistry. Outside of work, she enjoys
                        aquascaping, keeping ornamental fish, and spending quality time with her cats and parrots.
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="row align-items-center">
                    <div class="col-md-8">
                        <h4 class="mt-3">Dr. Joe Lin</h4>
                        <p>
                            Dr. Joe Lin is a dedicated veterinarian with a passion for providing compassionate,
                            high-quality care to pets of all ages. After earning his Doctor of Veterinary Medicine
                            (DVM), he has gained valuable experience in diagnosing and treating a wide range of medical
                            and surgical conditions in companion animals.
                            <br><br>
                            With a special interest in preventive healthcare, internal medicine, and soft tissue
                            surgery, Dr. Lin believes that early detection and client education are key to helping pets
                            live longer, healthier lives. He takes the time to understand each pet's unique needs and
                            works closely with owners to develop personalized treatment plans.
                            <br><br>
                            Known for his calm and approachable nature, Dr. Lin strives to create a comfortable and
                            stress-free experience for both pets and their families. Whether performing routine wellness
                            examinations, vaccinations, or more advanced medical procedures, he is committed to
                            delivering the highest standard of veterinary care.
                            <br><br>
                            Outside of the clinic, Dr. Lin enjoys hiking, photography, and spending time with his own
                            rescue pets. He is also dedicated to continuing professional development by attending
                            veterinary conferences and keeping up to date with the latest advancements in animal
                            healthcare.
                        </p>
                    </div>

                    <div class="col-md-4 text-end">
                        <img src="/images/drjoelin.jpg" alt="Dr. Joe Lin" class="img-fluid mt-4 float-end"
                            style="width: 300px;">
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="row align-items-center">
                    <div class="col-md-4 text-center">
                        <img src="/images/Dr-Ben-Lee.jpg" alt="Dr. Ben Lee" class="img-fluid rounded shadow">
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md-8">
                        <!-- Your headings and paragraph here -->
                        <h4 class="mt-3">Dr. Ben Lee </h4>
                        <p>
                            Dr. Ben Lee is a caring and committed veterinarian who believes in providing gentle,
                            personalised healthcare for every pet that comes through the clinic. With a strong
                            foundation in companion animal medicine, he is passionate about helping pets maintain good
                            health through preventive care, accurate diagnosis, and effective treatment.
                            <br><br>
                            His areas of interest include general wellness, dermatology, and chronic disease management.
                            Dr. Lee enjoys building trusting relationships with pet owners and believes that educating
                            clients plays an important role in improving the overall well-being of their beloved
                            companions.
                            <br><br>
                            With a warm and patient approach, Dr. Lee ensures that every pet receives attentive care in
                            a safe and comfortable environment. He continues to expand his veterinary knowledge through
                            ongoing learning and professional development to provide up-to-date treatment options for
                            his patients.
                            <br><br>
                            Outside of work, Dr. Lee enjoys exploring new places, spending time with animals, and
                            relaxing with his family and pets.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>

            </div>
</body>

</html>